PAINTERJS GENTLEMEN'S AGREEMENT & LICENSE

1. THE GENTLEMEN'S AGREEMENT
To maintain a healthy modding ecosystem and prevent version fragmentation, we operate under a "Gentlemen's Agreement":
Please do NOT distribute public forks or re-releases of this software unless the project has been inactive for at least six (6) months (no commits, releases, or bug fixes from Tazz).

If the project is active, please contribute your changes back via Pull Requests! We would love to have your help.

2. BASE LICENSE
Subject to the agreement above, this software is licensed under the GNU Lesser General Public License v3.0 (LGPL-3.0).

